<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        @page { margin: 0; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #0b1a2a;
            color: #ffffff;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .container {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            min-height: 100%;
        }
        /* Watermark */
        .watermark {
            position: fixed;
            top: 40%;
            left: 10%;
            font-size: 80px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            transform: rotate(-35deg);
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 15px;
            z-index: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .header {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .brand {
            font-size: 14px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: #00ff8a;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin: 20px 0 5px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #8fa1b4;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .status-badge {
            padding: 8px 30px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 13px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .status-en-attente { background-color: #f59e0b; color: #000; }
        .status-confirme { background-color: #10b981; color: #fff; }
        .status-annule { background-color: #ef4444; color: #fff; }
        .status-default { background-color: #6b7280; color: #fff; }

        .info-section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .label {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #8fa1b4;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .value {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #00ff8a;
        }
        .participant-name {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-top: 5px;
            text-transform: capitalize;
        }
        .divider-container {
            margin: 30px 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .divider-line {
            height: 4px;
            width: 45%;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .line-green { background-color: #00ff8a; }
        .line-purple { background-color: #6c5ce7; }

        .section-title {
            text-align: left;
            color: #00ff8a;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: separate;
            border-spacing: 5px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .details-table td {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: left;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-size: 9px;
            color: #8fa1b4;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .detail-value {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 30px;
            width: 100%;
            left: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .codes-container {
            background-color: #07121d;
            margin: 0 40px;
            padding: 25px;
            border-top: 2px solid #6c5ce7;
        }
        .code-box {
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            width: 45%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .code-label {
            font-size: 9px;
            color: #8fa1b4;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .barcode-img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: 60px;
        }
        .qr-img {
            width: 120px;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 5px;
        }
        .code-text {
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #00ff8a;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .scan-msg {
            font-size: 9px;
            color: #8fa1b4;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .legal-footer {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 8px;
            color: #8fa1b4;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="watermark">LAMA EXPEDITION</div>
    
    <div class="container">
        {# ===== HEADER ===== #}
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2613/2613317.png" class="logo">
            <div class="brand">LAMA EXPEDITION</div>
        </div>

        <div class="title">BADGE DE PARTICIPATION</div>
        <div class="subtitle">Document officiel — Accès événement</div>

        {# ===== STATUS ===== #}
        {% set statusClass = 'status-default' %}
        {% if p.statut == 'EN_ATTENTE' %}{% set statusClass = 'status-en-attente' %}
        {% elseif p.statut == 'CONFIRME' %}{% set statusClass = 'status-confirme' %}
        {% elseif p.statut == 'ANNULE' %}{% set statusClass = 'status-annule' %}
        {% endif %}
        <div class="status-badge {{ statusClass }}">{{ p.statut|upper|replace({'_': ' '}) }}</div>

        {# ===== EVENT NAME ===== #}
        <div class="info-section">
            <div class="label">ÉVÉNEMENT</div>
            <div class="value">{{ event ? event.titre : 'Événement #' ~ p.evenementId }}</div>
        </div>

        {# ===== PARTICIPANT NAME ===== #}
        <div class="info-section">
            <div class="label">PARTICIPANT</div>
            <div class="participant-name">{{ participantName }}</div>
        </div>

        {# ===== DIVIDER ===== #}
        <div class="divider-container">
            <div class="divider-line line-green"></div>
            <div class="divider-line line-purple"></div>
        </div>

        {# ===== DETAILS TABLE ===== #}
        <h3 class="section-title">• DÉTAILS DE LA PARTICIPATION</h3>
        
        <table class="details-table">
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <span class="detail-label">N° PARTICIPATION</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">#{{ p.id }}</span>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <span class="detail-label">STATUT</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ p.statut|replace({'_': ' '}) }}</span>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <span class="detail-label">TYPE</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ p.type ?? 'Simple' }}</span>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <span class="detail-label">DATE ÉVÉNEMENT</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ event and event.dateDebut ? event.dateDebut|date('d/m/Y H:i') : 'N/A' }}</span>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <span class="detail-label">LIEU</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ event ? event.lieu : 'N/A' }}</span>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <span class="detail-label">PARTICIPANTS</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ p.totalParticipants }}</span>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <span class="detail-label">MONTANT</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ p.montantCalcule }} EUR</span>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <span class="detail-label">GÉNÉRÉ LE</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ generatedAt|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</span>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <span class="detail-label">VALIDITÉ</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">Journée de l'événement</span>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        {# ===== CODES SECTION ===== #}
        <div class="footer">
            <h3 class="section-title" style="margin-left: 40px; margin-bottom: 10px;">• CODES D'IDENTIFICATION</h3>
            <div class="codes-container">
                <div class="code-box">
                    <div class="code-label">CODE-BARRES (Code128)</div>
                    <img src="{{ barcode }}" class="barcode-img">
                    <div class="code-text">{{ qrText }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="code-box">
                    <div class="code-label">QR CODE</div>
                    <img src="{{ qrCode }}" class="qr-img">
                    <div class="scan-msg">Scanner pour vérifier la validité</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {# ===== LEGAL FOOTER ===== #}
            <div class="divider-container" style="margin: 15px 0 5px;">
                <div class="divider-line line-green"></div>
                <div class="divider-line line-purple"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="legal-footer">
                <span style="color: #00ff8a; font-weight: bold;">LAMA EXPEDITION™</span><br>
                Ce badge est personnel et non transférable. Toute falsification est passible de poursuites.<br>
                Présentez ce document à l'accueil de l'événement — Code: {{ qrText }}<br>
                Généré par LAMA EXPEDITION™ le {{ generatedAt|date('d/m/Y') }} à {{ generatedAt|date('H:i') }}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
